Module it.polimi.ingsw.PSP034

Package it.polimi.ingsw.PSP034.messages.clientConfiguration

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnswerClientConfig
    Answer internal to the client, in response to a RequestClientConfig.
    AnswerIP
    Message internal to the client to select the address of the server to connect to.
    AutoCloseAnswer
    Message internal to the client that asks to close the connection.
    AutoCloseRequest
    Asks the client to close peacefully.
    ErrorMessage
    Message that communicates that an error occurred.
    RequestClientConfig
    Message internal to the client.
    RequestIP
    Request internal to the client to ask for the address of the server to connect to.
    RestartClient
    Message internal to the client that asks to restart the client.
    TitleRequest
    Message internal to the client that causes the title screen to be shown.
